"shrine" -> inform("[Keywords] Shrine of Eldan, Shrine of Elara, Shrine of Findari, Shrine of Oldra, Shrine of Bragon, Shrine of Cherga, Shrine of Ushara, Shrine of Adron, Shrine of Tanora"), "You can find nine here, of the gods: Eldan, Elara, Findari, Oldra, Brágon, Cherga, Ushara, Adron and Tanora."
"Schrein" -> inform("[Schlüsselwörter] Schrein des Eldan, Schrein der Elara, Schrein der Findari, Schrein der Oldra, Schrein des Bragon, Schrein der Cherga, Schrein der Ushara, Schrein des Adron, Schrein der Tanora"), "Ihr findet hier neun Schreine der Gottheiten: Eldan, Elara, Findari, Oldra, Brágon, Cherga, Ushara, Schrein und Schrein der Tanora."
town = Runewick, "Census" -> "The census office can be found on the secound floor of the building on Island of Spirit. You will find Torina Scibrim there. She will help you further."
